# 01 Data Inventory and Lawful Basis

## Intent
Require traceable mapping from each data field to purpose and legal authority.

## Mandatory
- Tag each personal/health data field with: category, sensitivity, purpose, legal basis, source, retention class, owner.
- Maintain machine-readable processing records for each mini-app and mini-app command surface.
- Enforce data minimization at schema and API boundaries.
- For high-risk processing, complete DPIA before release.

## GDPR-Specific
- Assign lawful basis per processing activity.
- Record balancing test for legitimate interests when used.

## HIPAA-Specific
- Mark PHI explicitly and map to allowed use/disclosure categories.
- Track workforce/business-associate access boundaries.

## Release Blockers
- Unclassified data fields.
- Undefined lawful basis or purpose metadata.
